biography: Thomas passion has been working with data since 25 years: from small databases for SMEs to large distributed systems for international enterprises and intelligent systems using machine learning. He graduated from the KIT in Karlsruhe, Germany and trained his first neural network while studying at UPC, Barcelona, Spain in 2002. Today he leads the Data Science & AI practice of BettercallPaul in Stuttgart and supports his customers and teams on their journey to generate added value from data.
